## reset-names

**Value type:** `<stringlist>`

A list of strings providing names for the corresponding entries in the `resets` property. Each string identifies one reset signal. The number of strings must equal the number of phandle+specifier pairs in `resets`.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
uart7: serial@880000 {
    resets = <&gcc GCC_QUPV3_WRAP1_S7_BCR>;
    reset-names = "qup";
};
```
